1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:03.480
US, US

3
00:00:04.100 --> 00:00:09.340
US, ALL OF US

4
00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:15.770
The end of the dream, the end of the sea

5
00:00:15.770 --> 00:00:17.750
We all have different places we want to go WE ALL HAVE DIFFERENT PLACES WE WANT TO GO

6
00:00:15.790 --> 00:00:18.530
We all have different places we want to go

7
00:00:18.530 --> 00:00:21.310
But to start we've got to show what we're made of

8
00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:25.660
We'll be legends, we're gonna take the world by storm

9
00:00:26.930 --> 00:00:29.250
Sparks are flying, NO LIMITS! This is where it starts

10
00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:30.530
ONE PIECE!!

11
00:00:30.890 --> 00:00:33.510
VORONOI START VORONOI END ALL OF US, I've got a question for you

12
00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:37.100
Have you let the world and all its burdens bring your dreams down?

13
00:00:38.740 --> 00:00:45.300
Every cell in me is getting restless - They're about to blow, oh, it's just too much Every cell in me is getting restless - They're about to blow, oh, it's just too much

14
00:00:45.410 --> 00:00:52.030
Still we try, ALL OF US have our own paths we cling to

15
00:00:52.030 --> 00:00:54.620
ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you

16
00:00:53.620 --> 00:00:55.150
ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall

17
00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:58.200
If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall

18
00:00:59.890 --> 00:01:02.580
Random clues suddenly fit together

19
00:01:02.580 --> 00:01:06.510
Starting to make sense, oh, what's going on?

20
00:01:06.510 --> 00:01:12.980
Threads of time weaving into an intricate tapestry

21
00:01:13.070 --> 00:01:18.680
We can't stop the world from turning, it's changing along with every one of-

22
00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.250
US, US

23
00:01:21.870 --> 00:01:26.360
US, ALL OF US

24
00:01:38.580 --> 00:01:40.660
You almost stepped on us, man!

25
00:01:40.660 --> 00:01:43.370
My bad, my bad!

26
00:01:46.460 --> 00:01:47.800
My...

27
00:01:47.800 --> 00:01:51.590
You've certainly grown...

28
00:01:51.590 --> 00:01:54.300
I'm not letting you take Apple Gramps.

29
00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:57.430
I'd appreciate it if you'd just...

30
00:01:57.930 --> 00:02:01.140
let me do my job, please.

31
00:02:02.350 --> 00:02:04.770
No can do!

32
00:02:17.950 --> 00:02:19.830
Whoa, now...

33
00:02:23.580 --> 00:02:26.000
Here we go!

34
00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:35.550
Go easy on me...

35
00:02:37.890 --> 00:02:39.890
if you wouldn't mind!

36
00:02:50.780 --> 00:02:56.200
<b>Luffy vs. Kizaru</b>

37
00:02:52.030 --> 00:02:54.450
Look at him go!

38
00:02:58.160 --> 00:03:00.160
We gotta run before it's too late!

39
00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:03.620
Yeah, while Luffy is keeping Kizaru busy!

40
00:03:03.620 --> 00:03:06.620
We'll have to be careful carrying Robin!

41
00:03:08.210 --> 00:03:11.050
Where are you going, Atlas?!

42
00:03:11.050 --> 00:03:14.510
I'm going down there to take back
control of the pacifista!

43
00:03:14.510 --> 00:03:16.180
Otherwise...

44
00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:18.220
as soon as the barrier goes down...

45
00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:25.140
they'll blast us with their lasers!

46
00:03:25.140 --> 00:03:26.940
What a capital idea!

47
00:03:26.940 --> 00:03:29.730
Vegapunk's the highest authority
on this here island!

48
00:03:29.730 --> 00:03:32.440
And whoever controls the pacifista wins!

49
00:03:33.940 --> 00:03:36.030
Damn right! I'm off!

50
00:03:36.530 --> 00:03:37.740
Wait, Atlas!

51
00:03:38.660 --> 00:03:40.740
Er, what I mean is...

52
00:03:40.740 --> 00:03:42.990
I... I'll go with you!

53
00:03:42.990 --> 00:03:43.620
– What?!
– What?!

54
00:03:44.370 --> 00:03:46.210
There's no way you're going!

55
00:03:46.210 --> 00:03:47.040
Why not?

56
00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:51.540
This whole thing is happening
because they're trying to kill you!

57
00:03:51.540 --> 00:03:52.630
Yes, but...

58
00:03:53.090 --> 00:03:54.670
Hey, Franky!

59
00:03:54.670 --> 00:03:56.800
Franky, can you hear me?!

60
00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.630
Yeah!

61
00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:59.800
It seems like Bonney is down there!

62
00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:02.180
She's alive?! That's great news!

63
00:04:02.180 --> 00:04:05.060
Kizaru kicked her hard—right into the barrier!

64
00:04:05.060 --> 00:04:06.810
He kicked her?!

65
00:04:06.810 --> 00:04:10.230
Aren't you a grown man?!
How could you let her get kicked?!

66
00:04:10.230 --> 00:04:11.690
I get it, man! My bad!

67
00:04:12.060 --> 00:04:13.690
I'll go save her right now!

68
00:04:13.690 --> 00:04:14.650
You'd better!

69
00:04:14.650 --> 00:04:16.780
But there's still the barrier...

70
00:04:19.030 --> 00:04:20.530
That's it! I'm going too!

71
00:04:20.530 --> 00:04:21.120
What?

72
00:04:21.620 --> 00:04:23.870
Edison can deactivate the barrier.

73
00:04:27.580 --> 00:04:29.210
Hello?!

74
00:04:29.210 --> 00:04:30.960
<b>Second Floor
Building A</b>

75
00:04:30.670 --> 00:04:32.710
This is Sanji speaking!

76
00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:39.630
If you're gonna rescue Bonney, count me in!

77
00:04:40.010 --> 00:04:44.350
Vegapunk. We've picked up
the luggage you mentioned.

78
00:04:44.850 --> 00:04:47.180
I'll head toward the rear exit!

79
00:04:47.180 --> 00:04:48.980
Let's all meet up there!

80
00:04:48.980 --> 00:04:51.230
<b>Below
In the Fabriophase</b>

81
00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.310
Report!

82
00:04:53.150 --> 00:04:56.400
We've all been turned into
children and seniors!

83
00:04:56.900 --> 00:04:58.110
Dammit!

84
00:04:58.110 --> 00:05:01.110
Stay away from the center of town!

85
00:05:01.110 --> 00:05:03.950
We believe the pirate Jewelry Bonney is there!

86
00:05:04.700 --> 00:05:06.910
She must be hiding somewhere! Be on guard!

87
00:05:06.910 --> 00:05:09.290
She'll manipulate your age!

88
00:05:09.290 --> 00:05:11.210
It's too heavy!

89
00:05:09.290 --> 00:05:12.420
Where'd that blasted kid get off to?

90
00:05:12.420 --> 00:05:13.710
She must be nearby!

91
00:05:13.710 --> 00:05:17.380
Find Bonney and take her out!

92
00:05:19.510 --> 00:05:20.510
Damn...

93
00:05:20.010 --> 00:05:21.970
Hey, over here!

94
00:05:23.090 --> 00:05:24.890
Sentomaru has been located!

95
00:05:25.430 --> 00:05:26.680
But...

96
00:05:28.640 --> 00:05:30.100
he's burned to a crisp.

97
00:05:30.850 --> 00:05:32.400
Sentomaru...

98
00:05:44.450 --> 00:05:46.910
S-Sentomaru!

99
00:05:47.290 --> 00:05:48.790
Bonney...

100
00:05:48.790 --> 00:05:50.370
Run...

101
00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:53.120
The Marines are coming...

102
00:05:59.050 --> 00:06:00.380
Sentomaru!

103
00:06:02.300 --> 00:06:03.510
What should I do?

104
00:06:03.510 --> 00:06:04.260
Was she there?

105
00:06:04.260 --> 00:06:05.050
No, sir!

106
00:06:05.050 --> 00:06:05.970
Go check that way!

107
00:06:05.970 --> 00:06:06.850
Yes, sir!

108
00:06:09.180 --> 00:06:12.230
Can I stay hidden until this all blows over?

109
00:06:12.770 --> 00:06:14.980
<b>Labophase</b>

110
00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:20.110
You're really going at it!

111
00:06:20.110 --> 00:06:23.110
Zoro! Want a hand?

112
00:06:25.740 --> 00:06:28.700
Just focus on Kizaru!

113
00:06:45.340 --> 00:06:47.430
If this is the best you can do,

114
00:06:47.970 --> 00:06:52.390
don't expect to get another shot
at facing our captain.

115
00:06:54.140 --> 00:06:55.650
Whatever you say.

116
00:06:55.650 --> 00:06:58.020
You're still an Emperor's right-hand man.

117
00:06:58.020 --> 00:06:59.980
You're well worth killing on your own.

118
00:07:14.790 --> 00:07:16.330
Seems like...

119
00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:18.920
I'm falling toward the ocean.

120
00:07:26.010 --> 00:07:29.390
Sacred Yasakani Jewel.

121
00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:51.490
What the?!

122
00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:57.000
– Sacred Murakumo Sword.
– Sacred Murakumo Sword.

123
00:08:18.270 --> 00:08:20.150
Ouch! That smarts!

124
00:08:20.150 --> 00:08:21.610
Gum-Gum...

125
00:08:24.730 --> 00:08:25.650
Dawn...

126
00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:28.740
Whip!

127
00:08:34.580 --> 00:08:36.120
It didn't work!

128
00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:37.250
Was it a holo-holo?!

129
00:08:37.250 --> 00:08:39.330
Which one's real?!

130
00:08:47.970 --> 00:08:49.180
Just kidding!

131
00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:50.630
Tricked ya!

132
00:08:50.970 --> 00:08:52.850
Gum-Gum...

133
00:08:52.850 --> 00:08:54.810
Dawn...

134
00:08:56.600 --> 00:08:58.680
Stamp!

135
00:09:11.110 --> 00:09:13.200
Did I get the real one too?

136
00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:23.920
I'm the one who got tricked!

137
00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:26.630
Now, that's strange.

138
00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:30.260
Where did Vegapunk go?

139
00:09:30.260 --> 00:09:32.590
Could you tell me?

140
00:09:32.590 --> 00:09:35.300
L-Luffy!

141
00:09:48.190 --> 00:09:50.530
Apple Gramps!

142
00:09:50.950 --> 00:09:54.740
Wait! Let me in, Vegapunk!

143
00:09:55.660 --> 00:09:57.160
What's going on?!

144
00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.580
You seem pissed!

145
00:09:58.580 --> 00:10:01.460
You better keep your hands
off her, you lousy Marines!

146
00:10:01.460 --> 00:10:05.080
I'm coming to save you, Bonney!

147
00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:08.710
How could I leave that innocent child to die?!

148
00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:10.300
Innocent child?

149
00:10:10.300 --> 00:10:12.170
Get in already!

150
00:10:12.170 --> 00:10:15.340
I'll let you ride with us!
Just squeeze yourself in wherever!

151
00:10:15.800 --> 00:10:17.510
Squeeze myself in?

152
00:10:26.190 --> 00:10:28.900
What are you doing?! Stay in the lab!

153
00:10:28.900 --> 00:10:31.320
You're gonna get yourself killed!

154
00:10:33.950 --> 00:10:36.320
Where do you think you're going...

155
00:10:38.410 --> 00:10:40.540
Vegapunk?

156
00:10:40.540 --> 00:10:43.040
Crap, crap, crap! We gotta move, Stella!

157
00:11:03.640 --> 00:11:05.060
He's back already?!

158
00:11:06.690 --> 00:11:07.770
Stella?!

159
00:11:07.770 --> 00:11:09.020
Lilith!

160
00:11:09.020 --> 00:11:11.820
Use the General Franky to carry the ship!

161
00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:14.400
I'll catch this ride and meet you there!

162
00:11:14.400 --> 00:11:15.910
You got it!

163
00:11:43.520 --> 00:11:45.230
Edison! Now!

164
00:11:45.230 --> 00:11:46.730
Comin' right up!

165
00:11:46.730 --> 00:11:48.190
Frontier Dome,

166
00:11:48.190 --> 00:11:50.060
partially deactivatin'!

167
00:11:52.230 --> 00:11:53.860
Initiatin' reactivation!

168
00:11:57.530 --> 00:11:58.990
We're falling! We're falling!

169
00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:11.750
H-Hey, look!

170
00:12:12.630 --> 00:12:14.210
Wait a second...

171
00:12:14.210 --> 00:12:16.170
I-I thought so... That's...

172
00:12:17.170 --> 00:12:19.130
Dr. Vegapunk!

173
00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:23.430
<b>Off the Coast of Egghead</b>

174
00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:23.430
This is the Fabriophase team on the island!

175
00:12:23.430 --> 00:12:24.720
I have a report!

176
00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:28.980
Dr. Vegapunk is descending
from the Labophase!

177
00:12:28.980 --> 00:12:31.360
Prepare to attack! Aim!

178
00:12:40.450 --> 00:12:42.200
Attention, all pacifista!

179
00:12:42.780 --> 00:12:46.790
Vegapunk has new orders for you!

180
00:12:46.790 --> 00:12:49.080
Wipe out every Marine...

181
00:12:51.130 --> 00:12:55.130
on this entire island!

182
00:13:22.950 --> 00:13:24.070
Oh no...

183
00:13:24.070 --> 00:13:25.740
It's our turn now...

184
00:13:26.790 --> 00:13:28.660
Objective updated.

185
00:13:29.290 --> 00:13:32.120
Wipe out all Marines.

186
00:13:37.050 --> 00:13:39.800
Get away from the pacifista!

187
00:13:48.430 --> 00:13:52.440
Vegapunk must have overridden their orders!

188
00:13:57.780 --> 00:14:01.450
Shit! I can't believe we lost the pacifista!

189
00:14:03.160 --> 00:14:04.910
Damn you, Vegapunk!

190
00:14:05.870 --> 00:14:08.580
That's the stuff, pacifista!

191
00:14:10.330 --> 00:14:12.960
Keep givin' 'em hell!

192
00:14:13.580 --> 00:14:15.960
Looks like it worked!

193
00:14:15.960 --> 00:14:16.880
Yeah!

194
00:14:20.130 --> 00:14:20.840
Hey!

195
00:14:21.220 --> 00:14:24.340
How are we going straight down?!

196
00:14:24.340 --> 00:14:25.930
Shouldn't we be falling?!

197
00:14:25.930 --> 00:14:30.180
A property of island clouds
is that they stick to each other.

198
00:14:30.180 --> 00:14:35.730
The tires on the Vegatank are made
of island clouds, so it won't fall!

199
00:14:36.110 --> 00:14:39.190
But enough about that. Atlas! Locate Bonney!

200
00:14:39.190 --> 00:14:42.190
She must feel alone and scared!

201
00:14:42.190 --> 00:14:43.820
Bonney!

202
00:14:43.820 --> 00:14:46.700
Where are you?! Bonney!

203
00:14:46.700 --> 00:14:48.120
Bonney!

204
00:14:48.120 --> 00:14:50.620
Bonney...!

205
00:14:58.210 --> 00:14:59.590
I have to focus!

206
00:15:00.460 --> 00:15:02.090
Feel her essence!

207
00:15:03.470 --> 00:15:05.130
I have to give Bonney...

208
00:15:05.430 --> 00:15:07.760
my entire heart and soul!

209
00:15:18.900 --> 00:15:20.820
I got a ping on my lady-dar!

210
00:15:20.820 --> 00:15:22.030
I found her!

211
00:15:22.780 --> 00:15:24.030
Where is she?!

212
00:15:24.030 --> 00:15:26.030
All I see are Marines!

213
00:15:26.030 --> 00:15:28.530
Are you sure, Sanji?!

214
00:15:28.530 --> 00:15:31.290
Has my radar ever been wrong?!

215
00:15:31.290 --> 00:15:33.160
Well, no...

216
00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:37.670
Scientific or not... I'll trust you anyway!

217
00:15:37.670 --> 00:15:39.040
Appreciate that!

218
00:15:39.670 --> 00:15:41.380
Although, this tank...

219
00:15:41.880 --> 00:15:44.840
is too slow to keep up
with my impatient heart!

220
00:15:47.300 --> 00:15:50.850
I'll be right there, Bonney!

221
00:15:52.680 --> 00:15:54.310
What a relief...

222
00:15:54.930 --> 00:15:57.190
The pacifista are on our side again.

223
00:16:08.070 --> 00:16:10.160
I finally found you!

224
00:16:10.160 --> 00:16:13.240
The pirate... Jewelry Bonney!

225
00:16:12.660 --> 00:16:15.620
<b>Vice Admiral Pomsky
Marine Headquarters</b>

226
00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:15.620
How dare you do that to my men!

227
00:16:16.870 --> 00:16:18.620
Found her! She's over here!

228
00:16:26.470 --> 00:16:28.430
Near-Death Experience!

229
00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:58.620
Hey! What happened to you guys?!

230
00:16:58.620 --> 00:17:01.710
I saw the river Styx...

231
00:17:03.540 --> 00:17:05.800
Get back here, Bonney!

232
00:17:09.930 --> 00:17:11.300
You will not escape!

233
00:17:13.930 --> 00:17:14.760
What?!

234
00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:17.020
Why?!

235
00:17:17.980 --> 00:17:22.900
It might be just the one, but I can control it
no matter what the authority hierarchy says!

236
00:17:24.150 --> 00:17:27.030
I command anything I ride!

237
00:17:24.900 --> 00:17:29.860
<b>Vice Admiral Bluegrass
Marine Headquarters</b>

238
00:17:27.030 --> 00:17:29.860
I'm a driver lady who ate the Ride-Ride Fruit!

239
00:17:29.860 --> 00:17:35.080
If I kill you, will it lift the curse
you placed on our men?!

240
00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:42.830
Dad...

241
00:17:42.830 --> 00:17:47.050
Give them back their proper ages!

242
00:17:56.350 --> 00:17:58.560
Bonney, you need to pay attention!

243
00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:02.140
Black Leg!

244
00:18:02.890 --> 00:18:05.860
Y'know, I heard Kuma is your father.

245
00:18:09.860 --> 00:18:12.860
But you have to remember
those aren't him! Or else you...

246
00:18:15.570 --> 00:18:18.080
Otter Hammer!

247
00:18:20.830 --> 00:18:22.620
They just keep coming!

248
00:18:25.210 --> 00:18:26.590
Guess we should run for it!

249
00:18:26.590 --> 00:18:30.090
Don't let them escape, pacifista!

250
00:18:31.800 --> 00:18:33.260
What?!

251
00:18:39.640 --> 00:18:41.680
Bonney!

252
00:18:44.520 --> 00:18:46.860
Sanji, Bonney! Get in!

253
00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:51.940
The pacifista are on our side now!
Let's head back up!

254
00:18:51.940 --> 00:18:54.070
Shake it off already!

255
00:18:55.070 --> 00:18:56.320
Ouch!

256
00:19:06.420 --> 00:19:11.300
<b>Labophase</b>

257
00:19:28.360 --> 00:19:31.650
We have our own reasons
for doing this too, you know.

258
00:19:34.860 --> 00:19:36.660
Don't care!

259
00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:51.630
Apologies, but if I spend all my time on you,
I won't be able to complete my mission.

260
00:19:56.720 --> 00:19:58.260
That's the idea!

261
00:19:59.430 --> 00:20:02.060
My mission is to waste your time!

262
00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:08.480
What to do...?

263
00:20:11.520 --> 00:20:13.110
Hold it!

264
00:20:26.370 --> 00:20:27.870
What's the matter, Chopper?

265
00:20:28.370 --> 00:20:29.750
Well...

266
00:20:29.750 --> 00:20:31.710
I'm not sure what it is, but...

267
00:20:31.710 --> 00:20:35.170
What is this haunting presence?

268
00:20:52.770 --> 00:20:54.730
What in the world...?

269
00:20:55.780 --> 00:20:59.070
Stand down, pacifista.

270
00:21:07.910 --> 00:21:09.080
What?!

271
00:21:09.080 --> 00:21:12.130
The pacifista have stopped escorting us!

272
00:21:12.130 --> 00:21:13.880
Come on, pacifista!

273
00:21:13.880 --> 00:21:15.840
You're supposed to keep us safe!

274
00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:18.260
I gave you an order!

275
00:21:19.010 --> 00:21:21.010
What's up with this?!

276
00:21:23.090 --> 00:21:26.430
The only ones above us
in the authority hierarchy...

277
00:21:26.850 --> 00:21:28.060
are...

278
00:21:28.980 --> 00:21:30.850
the Five Elders!

279
00:21:34.230 --> 00:21:35.400
Are we under attack?!

280
00:21:47.040 --> 00:21:48.500
A summoning circle?!

281
00:21:59.380 --> 00:22:00.550
What the hell?!

282
00:22:00.550 --> 00:22:03.050
Something's off! We need
to get to higher ground!

283
00:22:03.050 --> 00:22:03.760
Right!

284
00:22:07.640 --> 00:22:09.350
Attention, all Marines on land!

285
00:22:09.720 --> 00:22:14.810
St. Saturn of the Five Elders
will make landfall on Egghead shortly!

286
00:22:15.310 --> 00:22:19.530
No one below the rank of commodore
is permitted to behold him!

287
00:22:20.780 --> 00:22:21.990
An Elder?!

288
00:22:21.990 --> 00:22:23.450
I repeat!

289
00:22:23.450 --> 00:22:28.030
St. Saturn of the Five Elders
will make landfall on Egghead shortly!

290
00:22:35.830 --> 00:22:38.250
What the hell is up with that explosion?!

291
00:22:38.840 --> 00:22:42.590
The Five Elders?! One of them
came all the way to the island?!

292
00:22:42.590 --> 00:22:43.970
"Five Elders"?!

293
00:22:43.970 --> 00:22:45.640
Who the hell are they?!

294
00:22:45.640 --> 00:22:47.680
Only the highest authority in the world!

295
00:22:47.680 --> 00:22:49.100
What?!

296
00:23:11.950 --> 00:23:13.330
Something's coming out...!

297
00:23:39.730 --> 00:23:40.980
What is that?!

298
00:23:40.980 --> 00:23:42.480
It's a monster...!

299
00:23:42.480 --> 00:23:43.400
Don't say that!

300
00:23:43.740 --> 00:23:45.320
It has to be...

301
00:23:54.120 --> 00:23:55.870
The surface...

302
00:23:57.460 --> 00:23:59.290
It has been a while...

303
00:24:00.290 --> 00:24:04.260
<b>St. Jaygarcia Saturn
Godhead of Science and Defense
Five Elders, Highest Authority of the World Government</b>

304
00:24:04.260 --> 00:24:06.470
Is that some kind of monster?!

305
00:24:08.640 --> 00:24:09.640
Look up!

306
00:24:09.640 --> 00:24:10.600
Swerve!

307
00:24:14.270 --> 00:24:16.480
Oops...

308
00:24:16.480 --> 00:24:18.690
That was close...

309
00:24:18.690 --> 00:24:20.900
Oh no! The island clouds...!

310
00:24:23.610 --> 00:24:25.030
Kizaru!

311
00:24:28.280 --> 00:24:31.990
Hold it right there, Kizaru!

312
00:24:32.530 --> 00:24:36.910
You have to be reaching
your limit with that form by now...

313
00:24:36.910 --> 00:24:38.920
Please, Luffy!

314
00:24:38.920 --> 00:24:42.920
Do something!

315
00:24:49.630 --> 00:24:50.470
I'm on it–

316
00:24:57.310 --> 00:25:00.770
Gum-Gum...

317
00:25:03.690 --> 00:25:05.730
Star...

318
00:25:06.440 --> 00:25:07.150
Gun!

319
00:25:21.080 --> 00:25:24.170
Well now... this isn't good.

320
00:25:29.880 --> 00:25:31.340
Nika...

321
00:25:40.690 --> 00:25:42.480
Time's up...

322
00:25:55.370 --> 00:25:57.700
Are you okay, Vegapunk?!

323
00:25:57.700 --> 00:25:59.700
Not to worry, I'm alright.

324
00:25:59.700 --> 00:26:01.710
Atlas, are you hurt?!

325
00:26:01.710 --> 00:26:02.670
I'm fine!

326
00:26:09.710 --> 00:26:11.420
Are you St. Saturn?

327
00:26:11.420 --> 00:26:12.970
Indeed I am.

328
00:26:15.430 --> 00:26:19.890
I was certain we had
killed you already, Vegapunk.

329
00:26:27.230 --> 00:26:30.690
I gave you an order, Vegapunk.

330
00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:41.250
Bonney!

331
00:26:46.880 --> 00:26:51.260
You are not to leave him an ounce of free will!

332
00:26:51.260 --> 00:26:54.550
But if I do that, then Kuma...

333
00:26:54.550 --> 00:26:58.510
St. Saturn!
